author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by GameMaker, the free, fast, and easy-to-use 2D game engine that’s helped power modern classics like UFO 50, Antonblast, and Yahtzee’s Starstruck Vagabond – https://opr.as/SecondWind-3

On this week’s episode of Windbreaker, Yahtzee, JM8, and Marty celebrate 
March 10th, aka Mario Day, by choosing which four games featuring the iconic mascot that they’d choose over all others.
